{"tid":1159826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊: 修訂《逃犯條例》應是中共聖旨, 並非特區政府主意","createTime":"2019-05-18T04:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T04:37:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a970f6e93f806a2e6038656b99b13284bb4a70df","tid":1159826,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190518/59614099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F59614099&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkJODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=028c6f65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F59614099&h=742e566a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190518/59614099</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年05月18日<br />\n【引渡惡法】田北俊料修例早由中央提出：搞咁大壇嘢點可能係特區政府意見？ <br />\n<br />\n中聯辦昨日向港區全國人大、政協下令，特區政府今次修訂《逃犯條例》「一定要成功」，建制派今日起將在全港擺設街站撐修例。全國人大常委譚耀宗引述中聯辦主任王志民指並非干預，因中央不能不發表意見。前全國政協委員、自由黨榮譽主席田北俊認為今次港澳辦、中聯辦均表態支持修例，認為建制派會全部歸隊，但認為香港人大應代表香港市民而非為中央服務，如果同時為立法會議員，「要諗清楚」如何向選民交代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n田北俊認為，由政府提出《逃犯條例》修訂，認為「搞咁大壇嘢，點可能係你特區政府嘅意見？」指中央應該更早表態，以免讓建制派無所適從，他解釋指既然台灣表明不會接受有關修訂下作引渡，加上有多種現行方法可作出引渡台灣殺人案疑犯，故有關修訂是否有急切性？加上政府官員經常指修例是避免香港成為逃犯天堂，他又質疑是否有證據證明香港過去是否很多逃犯來香港，故當局必需急切作出修例。<br />\n<br />\n港區全國人大代表葉國謙出席同一節目時就指，昨日因公務未有出席會議，但他認為條例有爭議性，內地亦在修例上有角色存在，故中央表達意見是合適的。"},{"pid":"075b506c082fae903934c6967a52df6d956c2fbd","tid":1159826,"uid":71509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"玩完架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba02934d3543265344691d763276052347005d0","tid":1159826,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7a1e23b7f9d74f46702a35691de70d1f519ee2","tid":1159826,"uid":93000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"聖旨咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42a07ac34b68600138d4dbf1c36a52e0b84da32","tid":1159826,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"老母係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f9a487de019cf7bf8a405f26e46aa278efb046","tid":1159826,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人，做官真係易，市民又易呃同哄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b0999767a41c5cac2f3d00034e22110d9e2533","tid":1159826,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心大發現"},{"pid":"0c5498a53a816c72bba2d500e0be6a928b785240","tid":1159826,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:37:28.000Z","msg":"一國兩制無走樣無變形，因為根本不存在。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c0bbc598969ede903dd112d2bbbc8b05b490a","tid":1159826,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"咁係咪可以走得?"}]}